title: I-30 at SH 360 Interchange
text: Construction of the interchange began in April 2016. All main lanes and connection ramps were open to traffic on December 21, 2023, after 7.5 years of construction. Work on Six Flags Drive continued into 2024. In a future update I will add additional photos from the west side of the interchange.
